001package com.commercetools.graphql.api.client;

005public class TransactionProjection<PARENT extends BaseSubProjectionNode<?, ?>, ROOT extends BaseSubProjectionNode<?, ?>> extends BaseSubProjectionNode<PARENT, ROOT> {

009
010  public TransactionTypeProjection<TransactionProjection<PARENT, ROOT>, ROOT> type() {
011     TransactionTypeProjection<TransactionProjection<PARENT, ROOT>, ROOT> projection = new TransactionTypeProjection<>(this, getRoot());

016  public MoneyProjection<TransactionProjection<PARENT, ROOT>, ROOT> amount() {

019     return projection;

021

027
028  public CustomFieldsTypeProjection<TransactionProjection<PARENT, ROOT>, ROOT> custom() {

033
